I built a tip calculator
print("Tip calculator")
print()
totalBill = float(input("What was the bill?:"))
numberOfpeople = int(input("How many people?:"))
tippercentage = int(input("tippercentage to leave:"))
billwithtip = (totalBill+(totalBill * tippercentage/100))
totalBill = billwithtip/numberOfpeople
print("You all owe", totalBill)

